Template: percona-server-mongodb-server/postrm_remove_databases
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Remove all Percona Server for MongoDB databases?
 The /var/lib/mongodb directory which contains the Percona Server for MongoDB databases is
 about to be removed.
 .
 If you're removing the Percona Server for MongoDB package in order to later install a more
 recent version or if a different percona-server-mongodb-server package is already
 using it, the data should be kept.
